{"tid":2030163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民族自強，香港獨立","createTime":"2020-05-22T15:03:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T13:48:49.000Z","uid":63095,"like":81,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"848fb798f064e16b08480e09fd438c45de46cbe1","tid":2030163,"uid":63095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T15:03:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">講左好撚多次「香港獨立」係要放後面！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出處：香港民族黨<br />\n<br />\n香港民族黨以「民族自強，香港獨立」為目標，並提出六大主張作為黨綱：<br />\n<br />\n1. 建立獨立和自由的「香港共和國」<br />\n2. 捍衛香港人利益，以香港人利益為本位<br />\n3. 鞏固香港民族意識，確立香港人的定義<br />\n4. 支持並參與一切有效民主抗爭<br />\n5. 廢除未經港人授權的「殖民地惡法」，制定「新憲法」，必須由香港人制訂<br />\n6. 建立支持香港獨立的勢力，在經濟、文化、教育各方面成立以香港為本位的組織和政治壓力團體，奠定自主的勢力基礎"},{"pid":"86b2ec0606f7a3a14fa4c1a7a2a67a728ffc8d4e","tid":2030163,"uid":63095,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T15:03:56.000Z","msg":"民族自強"},{"pid":"3a9134398fb95850cb94a9e03493d49b5ff8548b","tid":2030163,"uid":63095,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"86b2ec0606f7a3a14fa4c1a7a2a67a728ffc8d4e","tid":2030163,"uid":63095,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T15:03:56.000Z","msg":"民族自強"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T15:04:06.000Z","msg":"香港獨立"},{"pid":"556e45001bebbee8240e9a2437e7630e4220fadc","tid":2030163,"uid":63095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a9134398fb95850cb94a9e03493d49b5ff8548b","tid":2030163,"uid":63095,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"86b2ec0606f7a3a14fa4c1a7a2a67a728ffc8d4e","tid":2030163,"uid":63095,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T15:03:56.000Z","msg":"民族自強"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T15:04:06.000Z","msg":"香港獨立"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T15:04:23.000Z","msg":"民族自強"},{"pid":"74364b0571b70cc04361638482239efa52dc4af0","tid":2030163,"uid":63095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"556e45001bebbee8240e9a2437e763